PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1988-1206 which will allow the CANADIAN BROADCASTING CORPORATION to enter into new leasing arrangements respecting the development of the underground retail complex at the BROADCASTING CENTRE in downtown Toronto, without the involvement of Cadillac Fairview Corporation Limited.
